{"ts":"2026-07-10T04:24:54.193Z","author":"codex-root-20260709","op":"create","patch":[{"op":"replace","path":"/body","value":"GitHub: https://github.com/unbraind/pm-cli/issues/488\\n\\nDuplicate evidence: exact all-status searches for GH-488 and path-target init follow-up commands returned no canonical item. Related historical pm-jek2 fixed caller-settings corruption, not generated next-step correctness. This item owns executable result/recovery guidance and an explicit workspace-target primitive."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/id","value":"pm-x26a"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/title","value":"GH-488: path-target pm init emits executable tracker-scoped follow-up commands"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/description","value":"Path-like pm init targets must emit follow-up and recovery commands that resolve the initialized tracker instead of assuming workspace discovery."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/type","value":"Issue"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/status","value":"open"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/priority","value":1},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/tags","value":["agent-experience","gh-issue","init","path-safety","token-efficiency"]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/created_at","value":"2026-07-10T04:24:54.193Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-10T04:24:54.193Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/author","value":"codex-root-20260709"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/estimated_minutes","value":120},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/acceptance_criteria","value":"Path-target init output and recovery bundles render executable --pm-path-scoped follow-ups; workspace-target mode creates <dir>/.agents/pm without changing legacy tracker-root semantics; SDK result contracts expose resolved target semantics; integration tests execute every emitted next step; docs and contracts remain aligned."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/parent","value":"pm-mpbb"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/risk","value":"medium"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/confidence","value":"high"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/severity","value":"medium"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/environment","value":"@unbrained/pm-cli 2026.7.9 path-target initialization"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/repro_steps","value":"Initialize a temporary path with pm init <path> --defaults, cd into that path, then run the emitted bare pm create/context commands; discovery incorrectly checks <path>/.agents/pm."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/expected_result","value":"Every rendered follow-up command targets the initialized tracker and succeeds exactly as shown."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/actual_result","value":"Bare emitted commands fail with tracker-not-initialized despite successful path-target initialization."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/dependencies","value":[{"id":"pm-3mna","kind":"related","created_at":"2026-07-10T04:24:54.193Z"},{"id":"pm-usfg","kind":"related","created_at":"2026-07-10T04:24:54.193Z"}]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/comments","value":[{"created_at":"2026-07-10T04:24:54.193Z","author":"codex-root-20260709","text":"Duplicate check: searched all statuses for GH-488, path-target init follow-up commands, initialized tracker next steps, and prior path-target fixes. No item owns executable post-init guidance; closed pm-jek2 covers caller-settings corruption only."}]}],"before_hash":"3cc22dff72be7b14824654a7a64ea62b04799939b2fee54c1b5f52ca60bf6df0","after_hash":"2785777c7893a2e0f4b8af74b1b43f2139a5a081a4f199cbb76dea44b70e1021","message":"Track GH-488 init target semantics without duplicating closed path-corruption lineage"}
